criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  female;

          -  ≥18 years;

          -  surgery for breast cancer (unilateral and bilateral) including ALDN with >6 lymph
             nodes removed;

          -  can effectively communicate verbally in Danish;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  surgery for breast cancer with SLNB or < 6 nodes removed;

          -  pre-existing lymphedema (primary or secondary);

          -  previous treatment for breast cancer;

          -  pace maker;

          -  conditions known to cause swelling (pregnancy, congestive heart failure, chronic/acute
             renal disease, cor pulmonale, nephrotic syndrome, nephrosis, liver failure or
             cirrhosis, pulmonary edema, and thrombophlebitis or deep vein thrombosis in the arms).
